Task 3: Clone the Google Homepage
Explanation:
Try to recreate the Google.com homepage UI using only HTML and CSS. Don’t worry
about search functionality — just design.
Focus on: Fonts, spacing, positioning elements like logo, search bar, and buttons


Index.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Google</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>

