Style.css
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
min-height:100vh;
background:#fff;
color:#202124;
}

/* Header */

header{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:15px 25px;
font-size:14px;
}

.left-links,
.right-links{
display:flex;
align-items:center;
gap:18px;
}

header a{
text-decoration:none;
color:#202124;
}

header a:hover{
text-decoration:underline;
}

.apps{
font-size:22px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.signin{
background:#1a73e8;
color:white;
border:none;
padding:10px 20px;
border-radius:5px;
cursor:pointer;
font-weight:bold;
}

/* Main */

main{
flex:1;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
padding:20px;
}

.logo{
width:280px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.search-box{
display:flex;
align-items:center;
width:600px;
max-width:95%;
border:1px solid #dcdcdc;
border-radius:30px;
padding:12px 20px;
box-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(32,33,36,.15);
}

.search-box input{
flex:1;
border:none;
outline:none;
font-size:16px;
margin:0 15px;
}

.search-icon,
.mic{
font-size:20px;
}

.buttons{
margin-top:30px;
}

.buttons button{
padding:10px 18px;
margin:8px;
border:none;
background:#f8f9fa;
border-radius:5px;
cursor:pointer;
font-size:14px;
}

.buttons button:hover{
border:1px solid #dadce0;
}

.language{
margin-top:30px;
font-size:14px;
}

.language a{
margin-left:8px;
text-decoration:none;
color:#1a0dab;
}

/* Footer */

footer{
background:#f2f2f2;
}

.country{
padding:15px 30px;
border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;
}

.footer-links{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
padding:15px 30px;
flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.footer-left,
.footer-right{
display:flex;
gap:20px;
}

footer a{
text-decoration:none;
color:#555;
font-size:14px;
}

footer a:hover{
text-decoration:underline;
}

/* Responsive */

@media(max-width:768px){

header{
flex-direction:column;
gap:15px;
}

.footer-links{
flex-direction:column;
gap:15px;
text-align:center;
}

.footer-left,
.footer-right{
justify-content:center;
}

.logo{
width:220px;
}

.search-box{
width:100%;
}

}


Features Included
Responsive layout for mobile and desktop
Google-style header navigation
Centered Google logo
Rounded search bar
Google Search and I'm Feeling Lucky buttons
Footer similar to Google's homepage
Hover effects
Pure HTML and CSS (no JavaScript)
